### Update author's own profile (author only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/author/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authorAccessToken}}

{
  "bio": "Updated biography for my own author profile",
  "website": "https://myauthorsite.com"
}

