### Add or update social media link (author only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/author/me/social-media
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authorAccessToken}}

{
  "platform": "instagram",
  "url": "https://instagram.com/myauthoraccount"
}

###

### Delete social media link (author only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/author/me/social-media/instagram
Authorization: Bearer {{authorAccessToken}}

